    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors were assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors achieved or exceeded their required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) is attributable to the standardized single-configuration nature of ASTM F1717 and does not undermine confidence in the validation conclusions. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-established acceptance bounds. The FEA modeling framework is accepted as sufficiently credible for the stated COU.",
